Class FileProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • FileProcessor

  • public class FileProcessor
extends java.lang.Object
    Basic scaffolding that simply breaks text in lines and invokes @see main.LineProcessor#process() on the main.LineProcessor interface. It relies on user-provided @link main.LineProcessor for implementing the desired line analysis
